channel.title: Curent Projects with no Audio Packs?
channel.description:
Auxy users like me buy AP packs use them for our projects. One thing came to me and thought to myself, _what do some of my projects sound like with no AP packs?_
This was the result: https://app.auxy.co/projects/txzZkUe2c0rVkyxfCprStg==
I'm interested in seeing what your guy's projects sounds like with no Audio Packs
